<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background: #f9f9f9;
            color: #333;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 900px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background: white;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        h1, h2 {
            color: #2c3e50;
        }
        p {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        .last-updated {
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: gray;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="last-updated">Last Updated: April 2026</p>

    <p>
        This Privacy Policy explains how our Grocery App collects, uses, and protects your information.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>
        We do not require users to create an account. However, when placing an order, we collect the following information:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Name</li>
        <li>Delivery Address</li>
        <li>Phone Number</li>
        <li>Order Details (products selected)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        The information you provide is used only to:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>Process and manage your orders</li>
        <li>Deliver products to your provided address</li>
        <li>Contact you regarding your order if needed</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Data Storage</h2>
    <p>
        Your order details and personal information are securely stored in our system and accessible only to the admin panel for order processing purposes.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
        We do not sell, trade, or share your personal information with third parties, except as necessary to deliver your order.
    </p>

    <h2>5. Security</h2>
    <p>
        We take reasonable measures to protect your information from unauthorized access, misuse, or disclosure.
    </p>

    <h2>6. User Control</h2>
    <p>
        Since there are no user accounts, you may simply stop using the app if you do not wish to provide information.
    </p>

    <h2>7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>
        We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Changes will be posted on this page.
    </p>

    <h2>8. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, you may contact us at:
        <br><br>
        <strong>Email:</strong> your-email@example.com
    </p>
</div>

</body>
</html>
